    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A soft cushion of loosely matted fibers of cotton, polyester, or wool, often distributed in a roll, used in upholstered furniture, cushions, packing, dollmaking, padding, and interlining in quilting.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047822/MFA Conservation and Art Material Encyclopedia Online: CAMEO (2005-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hoja o rollo de fibra suave ligeramente enmarañada, tradicionalmente algodón o lana cardados, utilizada para rellenar, acolchar y forrar al realizar acolchados.
</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Een vel of rol van zachte, enigszins gematteerde vezels, oorspronkelijk gekaarde wol of katoen. Het wordt vooral gebruikt als stopsel, opvulling en tussenvoering voor stikwerk.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052381/Van Dale Engels-Nederlands (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>由寬鬆編結的棉、聚脂纖維或羊毛纖維製成的軟墊，常常捲成一團使用，用於軟墊家具、坐墊、包裝、娃娃製作、襯墊或縫被夾層。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ein weiches Kissen aus grobgefilzten Baumwoll- Polyester- oder Wollfasern, das oft in Form einer Rolle vorliegt und bei Polstermöbeln, für Kissen, Verpackung, zur Puppenherstellung, Polsterung und als Einlage in Steppdecken verwendet wird.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
